# .dockerignore - keep the build context small and reproducible. Only the Go
# sources, go.mod, and go.sum are needed to build the binary.
#
# NOTE: do NOT add 'Dockerfile' here. Railway/BuildKit reads the Dockerfile from
# the uploaded build-context snapshot; excluding it breaks the build with
# "file with no instructions". COPY . . picking it up is harmless.
*.md
*.test
*.out
*.exe
live-fleet-grid
server
.git
.DS_Store
